        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Set in the 18th century, \"Red Sleeve\" depicts a love story between King Jeongjo and royal concubine Uibin Sung.\n\nSung Deok-Im is a court lady. She gets involved with Crown Prince Yi San and he falls in love with her. The crown prince eventually becomes King Jeongjo. He now desires Sung Deok-Im to become his concubine, but she refuses. Sung Deok-Im wants to live her life freely, something that will not be possible as a concubine. She also knows that life of a royal concubine does not generally bring about happiness. Yet, Sung Deok-Im becomes the concubine of King Jeongjo.",
            "source": "asianwiki"
        },
